title: Things This Preseason Has Changed Our Mind About
description:
Kevin and Nora are joined by Benjamin Solak to discuss recent NFL news, including the Gardner Minshew trade (2:40). Then they each discuss things they’ve changed their mind about now that the preseason is over (29:46).

Host: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
Guest: Benjamin Solak
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
